The first Mercurial burst onto the pitch in 1998 and since day one its evolution has been guided by one defining objectiveâ€”speed. Each design has built on the innovation of the one prior in a never-ending mission to make the fastest players in the world even faster.
 
Now, after over 20 years of progression, weâ€™re able to bring the bounce of Air to the speed of Mercurial for a boot that gives energy back with every step, cut, and acceleration. Extra snap when you need it most. 

Shop the latest merc at Nike.com
